name: [LORA] Cool Mix Style
description:
I made the painting style of the Cool Mix model LoRA.
It can create illustrations of very unique and beautiful faces and lovely designs.
I hope you enjoy it together.

这个可以制作非常独特、美丽的脸蛋和设计可爱的插图。
希望你也一起享受。
